  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的数据流图，核心是边缘节点和MQTT代理之间的交互。先从NFWB这个边缘节点开始吧，它要连到PM这个MQTT代理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，NFWB是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，PM是IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker。这两个之间是双向通信吗？还是数据从边缘节点上报到代理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是双向的，但主要是PM从NFWB收集数据，所以用双向箭头，不过方向上要体现PM是中心。然后TECH这个遥测流也要连到PM。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我把NFWB和TECH都连到PM上，都是双向关系。现在PM作为中心节点，接下来还有什么要连的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PM下面要挂三个下游模块：RES是PLC逻辑控制器，EMG是执行器控制器，还有一个NYSDEC也是MQTT代理，用于级联到上层。这三个都是PM下发指令或者转发的目标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，RES是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，EMG是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，NYSDEC也是IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker。这三个和PM之间是单向还是双向？看起来像是PM向它们分发数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都是单向的，PM作为中枢向下游分发。RES处理逻辑控制，EMG驱动执行器，NYSDEC负责向上级MQTT代理转发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，PM分出三条单向线到RES、EMG和NYSDEC。整个结构是左到右的流向，NFWB和TECH在左侧输入，三个下游模块在右侧输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了，NFWB和PM之间的箭头方向反了。应该是PM指向NFWB，表示代理去轮询或管理边缘节点，不是边缘节点主动上报到代理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，NFWB和PM之间的双向箭头调整为PM指向NFWB。TECH那边也需要改吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "TECH也要改，同样是PM指向TECH，代理去拉取遥测流数据。另外NYSDEC那里我搞混了，它其实是另一个MQTT代理实例，用于边缘到云的桥接，箭头应该是PM指向NYSDEC，表示数据转发出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部调整完毕。现在结构是：PM作为中心，左侧接收NFWB和TECH的数据（PM指向它们表示主动采集），右侧向RES、EMG下发控制指令，同时向NYSDEC转发到云端代理。这样符合工业物联网的分层架构了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这就是最终的拓扑。PM是边缘层的消息总线，向上对接云端的NYSDEC，向下管理NFWB边缘节点和TECH遥测，同时控制RES和EMG执行动作。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
